    {
      "id": "c41d65f1-6bee-4156-b16e-46daca23623a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors compare 2 embedding models combined with standard ML algorithms in terms of indicators of automated diagram assessmet reliability. The goal is to estimate the correct position of a student diagram in a causal chain.",
